 about  of its workforce  workers in january  at its peak a share of gopro was valued at  but on september   only  in november  the company announced it was laying off an additional  employees in an effort to reduce costs the company also announced that president tony bates would be stepping down at the end of  corporate actionsedit on march   gopro acquired cineform the acquisition included the cineform  video codec used in the film slumdog millionaire the company claimed that the codec makes hd and d editing faster and more convenient without sacrificing image quality it was incorporated in the companys d hero system shortly after the acquisition in march  gopro issued a dmca takedown notice to website digitalrevcom which had posted a review of its product citing trademark use as a breach of copyright this notice was retracted  days later citing erroneous enforcement on february   gopro spent  million and acquired two startups namely stupeflix and vemory for their video editing tools replay and splice ipoedit on february   gopro submitted a confidential filing for an initial public offering ipo with the securities and exchange commission sec on may   gopro filed its s with the sec without specifying the number of shares or their price the company stated that they hoped to raise at least  million through the sale of shares using the money to pay off debt in full  million as of march   and to acquire or invest in complementary businesses technologies or assets they said that they planned to list on the nasdaq stock exchange using the symbol gpro the expected price range was  to  a share on june   gopro sold  million shares to initial investors at  per share totaling m at the ipo price the company was valued at  billion  percent of those shares were allotted to loyal a technology platform that allows small investors to participate an important reason for gopros decision to go public was the potential to become a media company to generate additional revenue from the content its cameras create product linesedit hero camerasedit woodman worked on his first camera for two years after founding the company eventually introducing the gopro mm hero in september  at san diegos action sports retailer trade show in its first year gopro sold  worth of products in  the company introduced its first digital hero with  second video capability and generated  in revenue the following year gopro sales quadrupled to  million in  the company was selling the hero in editions of different colors it was capable of filming in  aspect ratio supporting k uhd video and mp still photographs the hero was introduced on  september  gopro karma  gopro karma gripedit gopro drone karma the gopro karma is gopros consumer dronecitation needed in  gopro entered into discussions with dji for a private label model built with the gopro branding after the failure of these negotiations gopro entered into an agreement with d robotics dr for a similar partnership based on drs flight controllers dr failed to meet their agreed upon timelines as a result gopro took full control of the development process in mid scheduled to be released early  the gopro karma project was delayed several times before the gopro karma was announced with an introduction date of october   the karma was released along with newer models of the hero and session cameras and features a removable handheld stabilizer gimbal integrated into the design after a few customers complained about power failure during operation gopro recalled karma drones and gave customers full refunds in february  gopro relaunched the karma drone accessoriesedit gopro produces various mounting accessories for its cameras including a way mount suction cup chest harness jawstype flexible clamp dog harness surfing mount etc video editingedit the company developed gopro studio simple video editing software to edit camera footage with v released in october  it was reported that gopro intended to also become a content provider also with a new app for the hero called gopro quik to share and edit videos easier content companyedit in april  gopro was listed by adweek as one of the top  best brand channels on youtube based on a combination of views shares comments and overall engagement content is uploaded daily an additional source of revenue for the company as part of its transformation to a media company in  gopro created additional channels with gopro content on youtube virgin america and xbox live this was extended to the playstation network in  hd hero camerasedit as of october update gopro sells three fixedlens cameras two without viewfinders and one including a touchscreen viewfinder a bit lcd on the front of the camera allows access to its menu system which is controlled by the front and top shutter buttons the hero black have dimensions of  mm ×  mm ×  mm and weighs  grams  grams with housing still images from  to  megapixels can be captured the cameras are sold with a clear polycarbonate hd housing with a glass lens that is rated shockproof and waterproof to  feet  m with a quickrelease buckle on the top and threads at the bottom to attach to all of the gopro mounts the housing has metal buttons that connect to the cameras controls and has a skeleton backdoor option to allow audio recording when the camera is used with a mount but without the need to be watertight or shockproofnonprimary source needed productsedit hero camerasedit mmedit the mm camera model  became available on april   it had dimensions of  by  inches  by  mm and weighed  pounds  g it included the camera a clear case with quick release a camera strap and ski glove adapter lash it could pivot on the fly and be functional to a depth in water of about  feet  m it was described as a reusable wrist camera and included a roll of  exposure kodak  film digitaledit the digital hero released in  model sq minicam had a × camera and shot vga definition x fps video for a maximum of  seconds the digital hero had  mb internal memory without sd slot digital edit the digital hero released in  had a megapixel camera and shot standard definition × video it was rated up to  m  feet in depth digital edit the digital hero was first introduced on december   it had a megapixel still photo sensor and supported standard definition × video capture it ran on two aaa batteries had  mb of internal memory and could function with a  gb sd card its housing was rated to  ft meters depth its dimensions were  ×  ×  inches  ×  ×  mm the camera is not designed to work with the newer hd hero line of housings although the standard screw mounts are indeed compatible digital wideedit this section is empty you can help by adding to it january  hdedit edit hd hero   shoots a maximum of p video and is not compatible with gopros electronic accessories although the camera is compatible with all gopro mounts it was first listed on august   lededit the hd hero naked released with a range of accessories shoots a maximum of p video on its mp sensor the naked camera line forms the basis for other bundles which are differentiated by the types of mounts they have hd helmet hero hd motorsports hero hd surf hero it was first listed on january   specificationsedit sensor size inch  mm ×  mm pixel size  μm image formats mode size fps fov r  ×   ° r  ×   ° r  ×   ° r  ×   ° r  ×   ° photo  ×   ° heroedit the hero was launched on october   it has an  mp image sensor improved lowlight capability and records at up to  fps it was sold with three different accessory packages as the outdoor motorsports and surf editions heroedit in late  gopro announced the hero line of cameras these new cameras came in three editions black silver and white all three versions of the hero come in a new  smaller and  lighter package with wifi functionality built in the change of the physical dimensions of the cameras compared to the previous generations hero and hero were physically identical means that some of the camera accessories for hd hero original and hero are not compatible with hero so gopro made new versions of those accessories specifically for hero and mostly for hero see below those new versions of accessories are usually not compatible with older hero camera generations however a lot of other accessories are compatible with all hd hero camera generations the hero silver and black cameras have significantly less battery endurance than the hd hero original and hero for example in p resolution with  fps while hd hero original and hero have a stated battery runtime of  hours hero silver edition has a stated battery runtime of  hours and hero black edition has a stated battery runtime of  hours the black editions most economical setting is p fps so this also partially contributes to its poor battery runtime the black editionnot in citation given has a new  mp sensor that can capture k uhd digital video at  fps k video at  fps p at  fps p at  fps p at  fps p at  fps and wvga at  fps the black edition also includes the wifi remote the black edition cannot record at  fps in p and wvga resolutions it can only record at very fast frame rates in those resolutions this is a deliberate firmware limitation as the manufacturer does not expect that this highend camera model will be used at these lower resolutions and frame rates the silver edition uses the same  mp sensor as the hero and the white edition uses the same  mp sensor as the hd hero original heroedit play media a timelapse recording one frame every  seconds with a gopro hero camera mounted on a bicycle helmet during a bike ride in chicago note how the wide angle lens allows for the rider to capture wide images in october  gopro released the hero available in black and silver editions replacing the hero generation the hero white edition remains as gopros lowend device the hero camera models claim dramatically improved low light performance and have a waterproof enclosure which is  lighter and  smaller than the heros according to the gopro website the hero camera housing is  smaller than the hero the cameras are claimed to have improved image sharpness close focus down to  vs about  ft on the hero at the expense of distant focus which is slightly less sharpclarification needed with hero and better audio functionality with wind noise reduction battery life is claimed to be  longer than for the hero model both through better efficiency and a highercapacity battery of the same dimensions the black edition has video modes of p p p and p as well as k and k and can shoot mp stills at up to  fps along with the increased resolution the hero black edition also offers an optional function in firmware called superview which increases the field of view it has additional functions including dynamic low light situation adjustment higherquality recording modes higher bitrates no white balance applied etc etc the black edition continues to include a wifi remote it does not have the ability to record  fps in p and wvga modes it can only record at very fast frame rates in those lower resolutions this is an intentional firmware limitation as the manufacturer does not expect a camera with its capabilities to be used at low resolution and frame rate the battery runtime of hero black edition is significantly longer than hero black edition but – lower than the battery runtime of the older hero and hero the silver edition has video modes of p and p and can shoot mp stills at up to  fps in contrast to the black edition the silver edition can record at  fps or higher in all supported resolutions hero silver edition also has about  longer battery runtime during recording than hero black edition they both use the same batteries the difference in runtime depends on the resolutionfps combination and whether wifi and gopro mobile application are used during recording the difference in runtime increases as the fps is lowered and the additional functions are deactivated on both cameras the battery runtime of hero silver edition is similar to the battery runtime of hero and hero the hero hd camera was awarded the  technology  engineering emmy award for its contribution to television heroedit gopro hero  silver edition in september  gopro announced the hero available in black edition and silver edition which replace their respective hero generation predecessors the hero session a budget camera was also announced the hero black edition still has a  mp cmos and a f fixed maximum aperture and focus free it adds bluetooth connectivity highlight tag protune available for photo and a new processor claimed by gopro to be twice as fast as that of the hero black edition doubling the frame rates in most resolutions the hero black edition can record k uhd video × at a frame rate of   and  fps in superview mode k is only possible at  fps many other rates and resolutions are available the hero black edition still shoots stills at a maximum of mp with a maximum burst rate of  fps with wifi disabled at k gopro claims the hero black edition battery life to be  minutes increasing to a maximum of h  at p the hero black battery is in a different form factor than its predecessors initial sidebyside comparisons of hero and hero black edition video results suggest that the newer model has more detail at long range and similar performance at close range the hero silver edition is basically a hero black edition with the addition of a micro speaker builtin touch screen display protune for photo and highlight tag the first gopro with this a lower clocked cortexa and missing the black editions integrated analogtodigital converter which supports a wider variety of professional lowsensitivity external mics the video modes supported by the hero silver edition are similar to those of the hero black due to the higher processing speed and thermal requirements of k video × but it supports wifi bluetooth and contains the same ambarella inc a soc as in the hero black the hero session released july   is  smaller and  lighter comparing to other versions of the gopro hero camera the hero models maintain the h video codec of previous versions and mp file formats gopro claims the mono microphone in both the black and silver editions has twice the dynamic range of the hero and that the hero black and silver editions have improved lowlight performance model hero session hero silver hero black sensor size    aperture f f f dimensions  x  x  mm  x  x  mm  x  x  mm weight  g  g  g with case  g  g with case still image resolution  mp  mp  mp video modes p p p p k k p p p k k p p p p photo burst fps fps fps connectivity wifi bluetooth wifi bluetooth wifi bluetooth water resistance  m  m with case  m with case touchscreen no  inches  mm x optional extra herolcdedit in june  the company started to sell a new camera gopro herolcd which provides video recording at p at  fpsand  megapixel photos gopro herolcd has a touch screen to preview the shot to frame the scene perfectly and letting user easily navigate the menu new feature in the camera instant camera editing gopro herolcd is waterproof because it is built directly into a waterproof case waterproof to  feet  m the device also includes a feature hilight tagging and builtin video editing function which allows user to put a label on the main points while shooting video or in the process of view which makes it possible to quickly find desired footage later technical specifications video resolution p  fps  p  fps photo resolution  mp   fps burst builtin wifi and bluetooth userfriendly modes like quikcapture superview and auto low light waterproof to ’  m builtin touch display heroedit in october  gopro released its third entry level camera gopro hero this camera has everything similar to the previous herolcd like the p  fps  p fps video resolution  mp   fps burst photo resolution builtin wifi and bluetooth waterproof up to  m and other modes like superview auto low light quikcapture and timelapse mode which automatically captures photos at set time intervals from  to  seconds however 