ly record at very fast frame rates in those lower resolutions this is an intentional firmware limitation as the manufacturer does not expect a camera with its capabilities to be used at low resolution and frame rate the battery runtime of hero black edition is significantly longer than hero black edition but – lower than the battery runtime of the older hero and hero the silver edition has video modes of p and p and can shoot mp stills at up to  fps in contrast to the black edition the silver edition can record at  fps or higher in all supported resolutions hero silver edition also has about  longer battery runtime during recording than hero black edition they both use the same batteries the difference in runtime depends on the resolutionfps combination and whether wifi and gopro mobile application are used during recording the difference in runtime increases as the fps is lowered and the additional functions are deactivated on both cameras the battery runtime of hero silver edition is similar to the battery runtime of hero and hero the hero hd camera was awarded the  technology  engineering emmy award for its contribution to television heroedit gopro hero  silver edition in september  gopro announced the hero available in black edition and silver edition which replace their respective hero generation predecessors the hero session a budget camera was also announced the hero black edition still has a  mp cmos and a f fixed maximum aperture and focus free it adds bluetooth connectivity highlight tag protune available for photo and a new processor claimed by gopro to be twice as fast as that of the hero black edition doubling the frame rates in most resolutions the hero black edition can record k uhd video × at a frame rate of   and  fps in superview mode k is only possible at  fps many other rates and resolutions are available the hero black edition still shoots stills at a maximum of mp with a maximum burst rate of  fps with wifi disabled at k gopro claims the hero b